exercises.description:
Use destructuring to extract values:
const arr = [10, 20, 30];
const [a, b, c] = arr;

Print a, b, c on separate lines.

Use the spread operator to combine arrays:
const arr1 = [1, 2];
const arr2 = [3, 4];
const combined = [...arr1, ...arr2];

Print the combined array.

